1329
01:40:51,700 --> 01:40:55,300
<i>All right! Whoo!</i>

1330
01:41:37,800 --> 01:41:40,100
Not that
anyone cares what I say,

1331
01:41:40,200 --> 01:41:43,400
but the restaurant
is at the other end of the universe.

1332
01:43:46,700 --> 01:43:48,000
Yeah!

1333
01:43:59,200 --> 01:44:00,600
Play it!

1334
01:44:59,000 --> 01:45:03,200
<i>It is, of course, well known
